quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  21,25,Kandi nta ntumwa twigeze twohereza mbere yawe (yewe Muhamadi) ngo tubure kuyihishurira ko nta yindi mana ibaho ikwiriye gusengwa mu kuri itari njye (Allah).Bityo nimungaragire (njyenyine)
  21,26,"Kandi (Ababangikanyamana) baravuze bati \"(Allah) Nyirimpuhwe afite umwana. Ubutagatifu ni ubwe (ntibibaho ko yagira umwana)! Ahubwo (abo bamalayika bita abana be) ni abagaragu bubashywe"
  21,27,"Ntacyo bajya bavuga batagitegetswe (na Allah), kandi bubahiriza itegeko rye"
  21,28,"(Abo bamalayika, Allah) azi ibibabaho n’ibizababaho, kandi ntibashobora kugira uwo bavuganira (Allah) atamwishimiye. Ndetse bahora bicishije bugufi kubera kumutinya"
  21,29,"N’uwo ariwe wese muri bo (abamalayika) uzavuga ati \"Mu by’ukuri, njye ndi imana mu cyimbo cye (Allah)\"; uwo tuzamuhanisha umuriro wa Jahanamu. Kandi uko ni ko duhemba inkozi z’ibibi"
  21,30,"Ese abahakanye ntibamenye ko ibirere n’isi byari bifatanye nyuma tukabitandukanya, kandi ko buri kinyabuzima cyose twakiremye mu mazi? Ese ubwo ntibemera"
  21,31,"Nuko dushyira imisozi ishimangiye ku isi kugira ngo itabanyeganyeza, ndetse tunayishyiramo inzira kugira ngo bamenye aho banyura"
  21,32,"N’ikirere twakigize igisenge kirinzwe, nyamarabirengagiza ibitangaza byacyo (izuba, ukwezi, inyenyeri)"
  21,33,"Ni na we waremye ijoro, amanywa, izuba ndetse n’ukwezi; buri cyose kigenda kizenguruka mu mwanya wacyo"
  21,34,"Kandi nta n’umwe mu babayeho mbere yawe (Muhamadi) twahaye kurama. Ese niba wowe uzapfa, ni bo bazabaho ubuziraherezo"
  21,35,"Buri wese azasogongera ku rupfu, kandi tuzabagerageresha ibibi n’ibyiza. Ndetse iwacu ni ho muzasubizwa"